		</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
		
		<div class="comment-body"><p>You are what you spew out Benjamin. And what ever you say from this point on is you, and you alone will wear it  Period. We have zero respect for blind, arrogant, haters who offer nothing but emotional garbage, and we further more have no desire to get on an endless merry-go round of commentary with them.</p>
<p>&#8220;I have surrendered as much to Abraham Lincoln&#8217;s goodness as to Grant&#8217;s artillery.&#8221;  Robert E. Lee </p>
<p>&#8220;The South has lost a good friend in Abraham Lincoln.&#8221;   ~ General Johnston, Confederate Major General.</p>
</div>

	</div><!-- #comment-##  -->

	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
		</ol>

		
	
